 ‚ÄúTesla Takedown‚Äù protests <a href=\"https://www.theverge.com/news/609621/elon-musk-doge-tesla-protests-us\">targeted Tesla showrooms</a> around the country to show disapproval for Musk, its CEO, who has spearheaded an effort to carry out mass federal workforce layoffs and hollow out government agencies. As <a href=\"https://www.theverge.com/news/641311/tesla-q1-2025-delivery-production-sales-slump-musk\">Tesla‚Äôs sales have plummeted</a> this quarter, <a href=\"https://www.theverge.com/tesla/638174/elon-musk-tesla-protest-free-speech-fox-news\">Musk has threatened</a> to ‚Äúgo after‚Äù the company‚Äôs critics, while <a href=\"https://nypost.com/2025/03/24/us-news/fbi-launches-task-force-to-nail-criminals-behind-fiery-tesla-attacks/\">the FBI has created a task force</a> to investigate individual acts of vandalism and other actions aimed at the company.</p>\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed is-type-rich is-provider-bluesky-social wp-block-embed-bluesky-social\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n<blockquote class=\"bluesky-embed\" data-bluesky-uri=\"at://did:plc:fctau3eedws5cdrvnv4k6n2q/app.bsky.feed.post/3lm3kdkkqss2b\" data-bluesky-cid=\"bafyreibdpdio3dnsv4l4yiffpqipijll23aud5bgw4dxlvyoulgg3pghjy\"><p lang=\"en\">Rain or shine (mostly rain)</p>&mdash; <a href=\"https://bsky.app/profile/did:plc:fctau3eedws5cdrvnv4k6n2q?ref_src=embed\">Mia Sato (@miasato.bsky.social)</a> <a href=\"https://bsky.app/profile/did:plc:fctau3eedws5cdrvnv4k6n2q/post/3lm3kdkkqss2b?ref_src=embed\">2025-04-05T18:21:40.575Z</a></blockquote>\n</div></figure>\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-none\">The scope of these protests is much broader, targeting both Trump and Musk, who the <a href=\"https://handsoff2025.com/about\">Hands Off website accuses</a> (accurately) of ‚Äúshuttering Social Security offices, firing essential workers, eliminating consumer protections, and gutting Medicaid.‚Äù <em>The Verge</em>‚Äôs Mia Sato is in Manhattan‚Äôs Bryant Park in New York City, where she took the above video. She told me it wasn‚Äôt clear how many people are there, but that it‚Äôs ‚Äúwall to wall everywhere‚Äù despite the fact that it‚Äôs ‚Äúraining here and really nasty.‚Äù</p>\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed is-type-rich is-provider-bluesky-social wp-block-embed-bluesky-social\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n<blockquote class=\"bluesky-embed\" data-bluesky-uri=\"at://did:plc:ylxn6kagok5e24tg4gvvngyh/app.bsky.feed.post/3lm3pqnjaj22d\" data-bluesky-cid=\"bafyreialq6bx6zxjh7sk7ommzewia2hwycg4h6ccasknn4y3dlico6x7ee\"><p lang=\"en\">Hands off rally in Washington, DC today</p>&mdash; <a href=\"https://bsky.app/profile/did:plc:ylxn6kagok5e24tg4gvvngyh?ref_src=embed\">Lauren Feiner (@laurenfeiner.bsky.social)</a> <a href=\"https://bsky.app/profile/did:plc:ylxn6kagok5e24tg4gvvngyh/post/3lm3pqnjaj22d?ref_src=embed\">2025-04-05T19:58:28.578Z</a></blockquote>\n</div></figure>\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-none\">My colleague Lauren Feiner, who attended the protest in Washington, DC, said the protest there ‚Äúis very big, thousands here around the Washington monument.‚Äù She described it as ‚Äúvery peaceful and orderly,‚Äù with attendees listening quietly to the speakers, occasionally chanting in response. </p>\n<img src=\"https://platform.theverge.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/04/HandsOff-Milwaukee1.png?quality=90&#038;strip=all&#038;crop=0,15.107333247095,100,69.785333505811\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" data-has-syndication-rights=\"1\" data-caption=\"&lt;em&gt;People gather to protest in Milwaukee, Wisconsin.&lt;/em&gt; | Photo: Jessica Toman\" data-portal-copyright=\"Photo: Jessica Toman\" />\n<p class=\"has-text-align-none\">Jessica Toman, who went to the protest in Milwaukee, Wisconsin, texted the above image to me. A person <a href=\"https://bsky.app/profile/kevinlikesmaps.bsky.social/post/3lm3fv52g6s2p\">posting images of the same protest</a> on Bluesky guessed that protesters numbered in the thousands. </p>\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-none\">It lo